'''Geeridu''' sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''dhimasho''' ({{lang-en|death}}; [[Af-Carabi]]: موت) waa marka [[naf]]tu ka baxdo [[jidh]]ka [[noole]]. Sharaxaada [[Saynis]]ka ee geerida, sidoo kale loo yaqaano ''dhimasho'', waa dhamaadka [[dhimasho|shaqada bayoloji]] ee suurtagelisa [[nolol|nolosha]] walax nool. Taasi micnaheedu waa istaagayso wada shaqeynta xubnaha jidhka iyo wixii ku dhexjira. Sida caadiga ah dhimashada waxaa keena waxyaabo badan waxaana ugu caansan [[gabow]]ga, [[nafaqo]]darada, [[xanuun]]ada, isdilitaanka (suicide), xasuuqida ama dilka (homocide), [[gaajo|gaajada iyo baahida]], [[biyo]]la'aanta sidoo kale loo yaqaano [[haraad]]ka, [[shil]]ka, dhaawaca iyo wixii la halmaala.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20101101081710/http://engineering.mit.edu/live/news/1223-must-all-organisms-age-and-die Leda Zimmerman. Must all organisms age and die? Massachusetts Institute of Technology School of Engineering; 19 October 201O]</ref> 

Jidhka noolaha geeriyooday wuu qudhma isla wakhtiyar ka dib dhimashada, wuxuuna ku darsamaa [[caro|carada]]. Laakiin waxaa mudo dheer sii jira [[laf]]aha iyo [[ilig|ilkaha]] kuwaasi oo meelaha qaar la helo lafo ama ilko jira kumanaan sano.

Guud ahaan geeridu waa mid xaq ah, sida [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka ah ku xusan qof walba sugaysa. Geeridu waa albaabka iyo wadada [[aakhiro|nolosha aakhiro]], waa mid lama huraan ah. 
Sidoo kale dhimashado waa arin murugo badan, naxdin, welwel, cabsi, iyo marooradilaac ku keenta [[qoys]]ka iyo [[qaraabo|qaraabada]] laga geeriyooday. Guud ahaana waa mid [[dad|aadamuhu]] neceb yahay.<ref>[http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?term=death Online Etymology Dictionary, 2013]</ref>

Sidaas daraaddeed markaannu dhimanno, jiritaankeenna wuu dhammaadaa. Kuwii dhintay ma fekeri karaan, wax ma sameyn karaan oo waxna ma dareemi karaan.<ref>[https://www.jw.org/so/tacliinta-kitaabka/suʼaalo/dhimashada-kaddib/ Dhimashada Kaddib Maxaa Dhaco?]</ref>

Waxaa taariikhda lagu sheegay in tirada dad ah ee dhimatay tan iyo biloowgii aadamaha ay ka badan tahay tirada maanta nool. Taas macnaheedu waa in dad ka badan 7 bilyan (dadka maanta ku nool aduunka) ay horey u geeriyoodeen.

Dhimashadu waa cadow oo kale. Boqortooyada Ilaahay baa dhimashada baabbiʼin doonta. Ma aha inaan ka cabsanno kuwa dhintay. Kuwa dhintay waxba ma oga, waxba ma dareemaan, ma ina arki karaan, waxba ma ina gaarsiin karaan. Ma aha inaan caabudno kuwa dhintay. Yehowah wuxuu leeyahay awoodda uu kuwa dhintay ku soo sarakiciyo. Dhowaan dunida jannay noqon doontaa. Kuwii dhintay waa la soo sarakicin doonaa. Mar dambe ma jiri doonaan gaboobid, curyaannimo iyo dhimasho.

